ns1:assessment-obstacle a skos:ConceptScheme ;
    rdfs:comment "A condition carrying wr:assessed false was NOT examined. It is not a condition that passed. This scheme names what stopped us, so that a consumer can tell an absence of evidence from evidence of absence - which is the distinction this whole store exists to keep." ;
    skos:prefLabel "Why a permit condition could not be assessed" .

